00.08.00 - 2018.02.19 05:22
	Following command-line parameters are available:
	 --config=file.ini   read the specified configuration file;
	 -s or --start       starts the countdown;
	 --run=command       at the end of countdown starts another program;
	 -e --exit           exit at the end of countdown;
	 -l nn or --lang nn  interface language (nn - the language code);
	 -h or --help        show command-line help.
	Possibility to set to exit at the end of countdown.
	Possibility to set to start another program at the end of countdown.
	Opened/saved configuration files are separated from default
		configuration file.
	Some code optimization.

